<TEXT>
   So many things are mind-boggling these days,
   Awe-inspiring and up-dated,
   That I do a lot of soul-searching to keep
   From becoming over-hyphen-ated.
   -- George O. Ludcke.
   ---
   Status Sleeper?
                                                                                                       

   Psychological inertia
   Is a phrase that suits me fine.
   It's nice to have my laziness
   Euphemistically defined.
   -- Mary McNorton.
   ---
   Daffynition
                                                                                                       

   Courtships: suits of amour.
   -- Lakenan Barnes.
